{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"27845493-d84b-4d8a-8f0d-52ccb2395020","content":"Yes, you'll hit compatibility issues. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**MSTest v3 dropped support for end-of-life frameworks.** Two of your three targets are affected:\n\n| Target | Status |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported (≥ net462 is fine) |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ Dropped — EOL since Dec 2022 |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ Dropped — EOL since May 2022 |\n\n**To migrate, you'd need to:**\n1. Update `netcoreapp3.1` → `net6.0` or `net8.0`\n2. Update `net5.0` → `net6.0` or `net8.0`\n3. Replace the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages with the unified `MSTest` (v3+) meta-package\n\n**Other breaking changes to watch for in v3:**\n- `[TestClass]` is now **strictly required** (v2 was lenient in some cases)\n- Some assert APIs have been tightened\n- `DeploymentItem` behavior changes\n\nWould you like me to update the `.csproj` to migrate?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"4f5049f9-12f4-4f56-b622-75191eca10f9","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a project that multi-targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. They want to migrate from MSTest v2 (2.2.10) to MSTest v3.\n\nLet me check MSTest v3 compatibility. MSTest v3 has significant changes:\n\n1. **Framework support**: MSTest v3 dropped support for older frameworks. Specifically:\n   - `.NET 5.0` is no longer supported (it's out of support from Microsoft)\n   - `netcoreapp3.1` is no longer supported (also out of support)\n   - `.NET Framework 4.6.2` (`net462`) - MSTest v3 requires at minimum .NET Framework 4.6.2, so this should be fine. Actually, let me check - MSTest v3 might require net462 or higher, which would be okay.\n   \nSo the compatibility matrix for MSTest v3 is: .NET Framework 4.6.2+, .NET 6.0+, and .NET 8.0+. This means the `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` targets won't work with MSTest v3, while `net462` should be compatible. MSTest v3 also consolidates its package structure.","outputTokens":722,"requestId":"7C21:2827DA:2AA6092:2FA018E:69F95A74"},"id":"632a11e3-4d84-4921-a0e0-f6d5bfbf70e1","timestamp":"2026-05-05T02:48:34.956Z","parentId":"c2084d8b-2136-48e4-b718-755098c4c19a"}
